name: Fizzbuzz Refactored!
tagline: Refactoring and Changing the original Fizzbuzz Project.
body:
The FizzBuzz game refactored:
* You can now add any number and it will generate the Fizzbuzz game for you based on your number choice.
Warning: Really high numbers.. (1,000 or up) can crash your overwhelm your browsers memory.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
